snippet.textDisplay: Just a simple masterpiece. Absolutely mesmerising and I am really lost on words to describe what I felt hearing this song. Being a mother to a toddler and one below 1 , managing work life and home together is a challenge that no one understands that what we go through on a daily basis. Sitting there defeated from the day and thinking that was a good mother today , I heard this song yesterday night. And just the words and voice of Shreya ji was enough to make me sleep relaxed in I think quite a long period of time.
